" data-state=\"closed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main-content\"><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden border-b border-border/80 bg-gradient-to-b from-secondary/40 via-background to-background\" aria-labelledby=\"hero-heading\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-accent/10 via-transparent to-transparent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-10 px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 md:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] md:items-center md:py-24\"><div class=\"relative z-10\" style=\"opacity:0\"><p class=\"font-display text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-accent\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Gulu University</p><h1 id=\"hero-heading\" class=\"mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"> Kisa Christopher Ebenezer</h1><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-xl text-lg text-muted-foreground md:text-xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Lecturer, Faculty of Education and Humanities <!-- -->. <!-- -->12+ years of university teaching with 40+ peer-reviewed publications; . Passionate about evidence-based pedagogy and community-engaged research.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><a aria-label=\"View publications\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow hover:bg-primary/90 h-11 rounded-md px-8 gap-2\" href=\"/publications\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg>Publications<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a aria-label=\"Get in touch\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border border-input bg-background shadow-sm hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground h-11 rounded-md px-8 gap-2\" href=\"/contact\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail h-4 w-4\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"16\" x=\"2\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7\"></path></svg>Contact</a></div></div><div class=\"relative z-0 mx-auto w-full max-w-md md:max-w-none\" style=\"opacity:1;transform:none\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border bg-muted shadow-2xl shadow-primary/10 ring-1 ring-black/5 dark:ring-white/10\"><img alt=\"Professional portrait of  Kisa Christopher Ebenezer\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 768px) 40vw, 90vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097-0b93528c311a%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D900%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D80&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097-0b93528c311a%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D900%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D80&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097-0b93528c311a%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D900%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D80&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097-0b93528c311a%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D900%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D80&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097-0b93528c311a%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D900%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D80&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097-0b93528c311a%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D900%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D80&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097-0b93528c311a%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D900%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D80&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097-0b93528c311a%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D900%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D80&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097-0b93528c311a%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D900%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D80&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097-0b93528c311a%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D900%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097-0b93528c311a%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D900%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background/40 to-transparent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-6 -left-4 hidden rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/95 p-4 shadow-lg backdrop-blur sm:block md:-left-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><p class=\"font-display text-2xl font-bold text-primary dark:text-primary-foreground\"></p><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\"></p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-t border-border/80 bg-muted/20 py-16\" aria-labelledby=\"research-highlights-heading\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6\"><h2 id=\"research-highlights-heading\" class=\"font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Research highlights</h2><p class=\"mt-2 max-w-2xl text-muted-foreground\">Themes that shape teaching, mentoring, and collaborations across Northern Uganda and beyond.</p><div class=\"mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full border-border/80 bg-card/80 backdrop-blur\"><div class=\"space-y-3 p-6\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-microscope h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 18h8\"></path><path d=\"M3 22h18\"></path><path d=\"M14 22a7 7 0 1 0 0-14h-1\"></path><path d=\"M9 14h2\"></path><path d=\"M9 12a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6h6v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2Z\"></path><path d=\"M12 6V3a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H9a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v3\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-semibold\">Community-engaged interventions</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\">Designing stigma-reduction and resilience programs with local partners and student co-researchers.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full border-border/80 bg-card/80 backdrop-blur\"><div class=\"space-y-3 p-6\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-semibold\">Higher-education wellbeing</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\">Longitudinal work on sleep, screen use, and academic engagement in resource-conscious settings.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full border-border/80 bg-card/80 backdrop-blur\"><div class=\"space-y-3 p-6\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-marked h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 2v8l3-3 3 3V2\"></path><path d=\"M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H19a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v18a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H6.5a1 1 0 0 1 0-5H20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-semibold\">Open scholarship</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\">Preregistered studies, replication-friendly materials, and mentoring in transparent methods.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6\" aria-labelledby=\"latest-pubs-heading\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-4\"><div><h2 id=\"latest-pubs-heading\" class=\"font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Latest publications</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted-foreground\">Recent peer-reviewed work — explore the full list with live filters.</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border border-input bg-background shadow-sm hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground h-10 px-4 py-2\" href=\"/publications\">All publications</a></div><ul class=\"mt-8 space-y-4\"><li><div class=\"rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4 p-6\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-semibold leading-snug\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"hover:text-accent transition-colors\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1000/jcp.2024.001\">Trauma-Informed Classrooms in Post-Conflict Northern Uganda: A Longitudinal Study</a></h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Ebenezer, C. K., Acen, J., &amp; Okello, D.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-medium\">Journal of Community Psychology<!-- --> · <!-- -->2024</p></div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-md border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-accent text-accent-foreground hover:bg-accent/80\">journal</div></div></div></li><li><div class=\"rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4 p-6\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-semibold leading-snug\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"hover:text-accent transition-colors\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1000/edpr.2023.882\">Executive Function Training and Mathematics Outcomes in Adolescent Learners</a></h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Ebenezer, C. K., Naluwooza, P.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-medium\">Educational Psychology Review<!-- --> · <!-- -->2023</p></div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-md border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-accent text-accent-foreground hover:bg-accent/80\">journal</div></div></div></li><li><div class=\"rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4 p-6\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-semibold leading-snug\">Stigma Reduction Interventions for Help-Seeking in Rural African Universities</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Ochieng, M., Ebenezer, C. K., et al.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-medium\">Proceedings of the International Conference on Higher Education Psychology<!-- --> · <!-- -->2023</p></div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-md border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-accent text-accent-foreground hover:bg-accent/80\">conference</div></div></div></li></ul></section><section class=\"border-t border-border/80 bg-secondary/25 py-16\" aria-labelledby=\"blog-preview-heading\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-4\"><div><h2 id=\"blog-preview-heading\" class=\"font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">From the blog</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted-foreground\">Notes on teaching, methods, and field work — published as MDX.</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-accent text-accent-foreground shadow hover:bg-accent/90 h-10 px-4 py-2\" href=\"/blog\">Visit blog</a></div><div class=\"mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full border-border/80 transition-all duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex flex-col space-y-1.5 p-6\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-md border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80\">Teaching</div><div class=\"font-display font-semibold text-xl\"><a class=\"hover:text-accent\" href=\"/blog/open-science-in-the-classroom\">Open science in the psychology classroom</a></div></div><div class=\"p-6 pt-0\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Practical ways to bring preregistration and data literacy into undergraduate labs without overwhelming students.</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">15/01/2025</p></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full border-border/80 transition-all duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex flex-col space-y-1.5 p-6\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-md border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80\">Teaching</div><div class=\"font-display font-semibold text-xl\"><a class=\"hover:text-accent\" href=\"/blog/trauma-informed-syllabus-design\">Trauma-informed syllabus design (that still has standards)</a></div></div><div class=\"p-6 pt-0\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Balancing rigor with predictability, choice, and care—especially after community disruption.</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">02/11/2024</p></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full border-border/80 transition-all duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex flex-col space-y-1.5 p-6\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-md border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80\">Research</div><div class=\"font-display font-semibold text-xl\"><a class=\"hover:text-accent\" href=\"/blog/field-notes-from-gulu\">Field notes from community listening sessions in Gulu</a></div></div><div class=\"p-6 pt-0\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">What we heard when we slowed down, translated carefully, and paid facilitators as experts.</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">18/09/2024</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/5 via-background to-accent/5\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 p-8 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between\"><div><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-bold\">Collaborate with <!-- --> Kisa Christopher Ebenezer</h2><p class=\"mt-2 max-w-xl text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Guest lectures, joint grants, graduate supervision, and community projects — reach out with a short outline of your idea.</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow hover:bg-primary/90 h-11 rounded-md px-8\" href=\"/contact\">Schedule a conversation</a></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-border/80 bg-muted/30\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-8 px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between\"><div><p class=\"font-display text-lg font-semibold text-foreground\"> Kisa Christopher Ebenezer</p><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Lecturer, Faculty of Education and Humanities <!-- --> · <!-- -->Gulu University</p><p class=\"mt-2 max-w-md text-sm text-muted-foreground\">12+ years of university teaching with 40+ peer-reviewed publications; . Passionate about evidence-based pedagogy and community-engaged research.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border bg-background px-4 text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:text-accent\" aria-label=\"LinkedIn\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-linkedin h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v